# Revora project rules

- Monorepo: `revora-frontend/` (Shopify app), `revora-extension/` (Chrome extension)
- Use **Bun** only (`bun install`, `bun run`). Never npm/yarn/pnpm
- Keep changes focused; no drive-by refactors or unsolicited markdown docs
- Never commit secrets (`.env.local`, Turso tokens, Shopify secrets)
- API changes must update frontend routes **and** extension `background.js`
- Pairing code format: `REVORA1.<base64>` — keep `pairing-code.ts` and `pairing.js` aligned
- Dev tunnel URLs change on restart; extension syncs URL from Shopify admin, not a fixed host